This code is provided with the CMake build system.
In order to compile the code & install, make sure you have installed both GSL & FFTW3 libraries.
Under standard installation process, just type

cd build/
cmake ..
make
make install

If you have special build requirements, check

cmake --help

If you want to delete temporary files & all the products of compilation, just type

cd build/
make clean
rm -rf *

It is recommended to use gsl-1.15 & fftw-3.3.2 or more recent versions
